sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    box Purple Client Side
        actor U as User
        participant SPA as Single-Page App
    end
    box Green Authorization Server
        participant AS as Auth Server
        participant TS as Token Service
    end
    participant API as Resource API

    U->>+SPA: Click "Log in"
    Note over SPA: Generate code_verifier<br/>and code_challenge (S256)
    SPA->>+AS: GET /authorize?challenge=...
    AS-->>U: Show consent screen
    U->>AS: Approve scopes
    AS-->>-SPA: 302 redirect + auth_code

    rect rgb(40, 60, 90)
        Note over SPA,TS: Token exchange (back channel)
        SPA->>+TS: POST /token (auth_code + code_verifier)
        TS->>TS: Verify PKCE challenge
        alt verifier valid
            TS-->>SPA: access_token + refresh_token
        else verifier mismatch
            TS-->>SPA: 400 invalid_grant
        end
        deactivate TS
    end

    opt Token received
        SPA->>+API: GET /me (Bearer access_token)
        API->>API: Validate JWT signature
        API-->>-SPA: 200 user profile
    end

    SPA-->>-U: Render dashboard
